value.0: This figure is adorned in a heavy black robe and an equally dark cowl that seems to obscure his features.  In his hand is clutched a book that seems frail and decrepit, alongside a quill.
This is a leather hood, which should provide a minor amount of protection from blows.
This finely crafted suit of full plate mail is several centuries old, but due to its lasting enchantments it is ready for battle as ever.
Piecemeal or complete armors of this type offer protection equivalent to a suit of full plate armor.
This old cloak was worn by lords in ancient times.  Although the finery that once decorated it is lost to time, it may be of value to a historian.
